Welcome to Seeds

What is Seeds?

AI-Driven Stock Analyser. Uses AI to analyse stocks by sentiment, financial fundamentals and market conditions.

How does it work?

Seeds uses LLMs to assess sentiment across sources like reddit, uses financial metrics to assess basic health of a company and then looks at technical indicators.

Who is it for?

Built to make the stock market accessible to a layman. This is for someone who wants to invest smartly.
